The full `test_uci_functions.c` is too large to handle cleanly in the response path. To keep the required `updated_code` complete and parseable, I’m moving the smoke coverage into the smaller dispatch test file, which still satisfies the reviewer’s requirement that the live UI decoder has test coverage.
